name: Saving Grace - The Urgency (Exclusive New Zealand Pre Order) CD
description:
Exclusive New Zealand only pre-order includes FREE postage. Strictly limited to 100 only.

'The Urgency' is the brand new highly anticipated full length album from New Zealand heavyweights Saving Grace.

Produced & Engineered by Zack Ohren (All Shall Perish, The Ghost Inside, Carnifex, First Blood).

Available In stores & Online on Deadboy Records / Universal Music January 21st.

TRACKLISTING:

1. +0
2. Like A Trainwreck
3. 1994
4. Descent
5. Horse Apples
6. The Banks Of The Otara
7. Was:Is 
8. Ceremony
9. Anthem Of The Underground
10. Temple Of The Snake
11. The Man Who Painted The Pavement
12. Ablaze
13. The Urgency
